                    %p FOUNDER AND CTO
                    %i.ico.ico-border

                  .profile-body
                    %p Business Builder. Outdoor Adventure. The meaning of life. Practical Joker, with a serious side.

                  .profile-foot
                    %p
                      %strong STRENGTH:
                      Relentless
                      %br/
